Package: libbc-core-dev
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: bc-* ecosystem core C primitives (development files)
 Cache-line-aware memory helpers, SIMD-accelerated byte search,
 integer-safe math with overflow checks, and CPU-dispatched hash
 primitives (SHA-256 with SHA-NI fast path, CRC32C via SSE4.2).
 The foundation every other bc-* library builds on.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-core.
